data.title: C Logs Pop Flash For C Long
data.description: This is a great FLASH/DRIVE to pop flash players pushing out of C Long into C Site.

data.title: Top C Long ZERO/POINT From C Site
data.description: This is a great ZERO/POINT to catch players at the top of C Long who are pushing into C Site off guard and suppress them, since the ZERO/POINT quickly lands in a spot that is difficult to react to, especially if you haven't seen the ZERO/POINT land there before.
